{"tid":1594953,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓漫《看臉時代》確認翻拍陸劇！　男主角是他？","createTime":"2019-09-25T22:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T00:48:28.000Z","uid":88491,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"dbfe5b167e5345492e2a6d03a0fbaaf3f61d6ed2","tid":1594953,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T22:45:25.000Z","msg":"南韓超人氣網路漫畫《看臉時代》翻拍陸劇《外貌至上主義》，男主角由《復仇筆記》的朴所羅門擔綱，該劇定檔26日開播，近日釋出2分鐘預告影片，引起網友的高度關注。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TSWnoBk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTSWnoBk.png&h=b58c65d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲電視劇《外貌至上主義》改編自網路漫畫《看臉時代》。（圖／翻攝LINE WEBTOON、微博）<br />\n漫畫《看臉時代》在南韓擁有超高人氣，劇情描述全校最遜的男生一夜之間變成人氣校草的故事，圈粉無數，還曾在台灣《LINE WEBTOON》漫畫APP上蟬聯許久的觀看數第一。除了劇情引人入勝外，作者朴泰俊以身邊的朋友、家人做為角色原型，讓《看臉時代》多了一個看點，其中男主角便是作者以親弟弟「朴亨錫」為原型所畫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QVY5mn4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQVY5mn4.png&h=72987133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲《看臉時代》男主角原型是作者弟弟。（圖／翻攝朴亨錫IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sihmD9P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsihmD9P.jpg&h=bf2d11ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲《看臉時代》男主角原型是作者弟弟朴亨錫。（圖／翻攝朴亨錫IG）<br />\n電視劇《外貌至上主義》描述一個又醜又胖的男子「文帥」因在學校被霸凌，鼓起勇氣轉學，卻在一夜之間擁有了兩個迥然不同的身體，一個是醜胖的自己，另一個竟是「顏值爆表的完美男神」。飾演「男神版文帥」的朴所羅門，現年19歲，曾與車銀優、《與神同行》的金香起一同演出《復仇筆記》，為第一男主角，演技頗受肯定，許多觀眾都相當期待他如何詮釋此次角色。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔能係呀話，我等左咁耐翻拍 變能左19大陸劇但男主角又搵個韓仔拍 乜能野事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f676a9acae9a06928862c1012e4c1843e228b316","tid":1594953,"uid":256952,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T22:46:45.000Z","msg":"仆街 大6佬 又搞破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa17cbfff06781ca5b75d282189b6b8eb22b828","tid":1594953,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f676a9acae9a06928862c1012e4c1843e228b316","tid":1594953,"uid":256952,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T22:46:45.000Z","msg":"仆街 大6佬 又搞破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T22:53:31.000Z","msg":"痴線 點估到變左大陸劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8416775b5ef12b555ed6fa0b98ecbb94f8b218c4","tid":1594953,"uid":71237,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T22:57:22.000Z","msg":"漫畫都越嚟越爛，無啦啦講四大聯盟變咗格鬥漫。<br />\n人物多到唔認得。"},{"pid":"6ece7c1dafba8e20e0102f4dcee15a80fb7ae31b","tid":1594953,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T23:11:49.000Z","msg":"朴所羅門<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f51adcf2eda668c87486ebbfe5fff41584b0c6c","tid":1594953,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ece7c1dafba8e20e0102f4dcee15a80fb7ae31b","tid":1594953,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T23:11:49.000Z","msg":"朴所羅門<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T23:19:51.000Z","msg":"屌  搵佢做男主真係一般 成件事錯曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11399fca049a3df77e4fa48af49de36bd81035da","tid":1594953,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8416775b5ef12b555ed6fa0b98ecbb94f8b218c4","tid":1594953,"uid":71237,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T22:57:22.000Z","msg":"漫畫都越嚟越爛，無啦啦講四大聯盟變咗格鬥漫。<br />\n人物多到唔認得。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T23:20:23.000Z","msg":"去到後期我都無追 但前面